metadata.name: Horses and Ballerina
metadata.description:
Turkey is known as the land of beautiful horses. The ballerina dances the performer wildly among the horses tirelessly . 

''Dans has nothing to prove. I have never used dance as a beat or a form of expression. I'm just dancing. I just lift the feet and play.''  - Fred Astaire


Artist: Kahraman Bekcili 
Dimensions: 4800 × 3200 
Resolution: 300dpi
Location: Kapadokya / Turkey 
Date: 16/07/2022 
Print:1/1
